==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lithology
<hw>Li*thol"o*gy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Litho-</ets> + <ets>-logy</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>lithologie</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The science which treats
of rocks, as regards their mineral constitution and classification, and
their mode of occurrence in nature.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A treatise on stones found in the
body.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lithomancy</ent>⟦br⟧
